* PROMOTIONS Dictionary Definitions
* MultiValue Database Schema for Promotional Campaigns and Rules

* Field Definitions
FIELD~PROMO.ID~1~Promotion ID~Primary Key
FIELD~PROMO.CODE~2~Promotion Code~User-facing code
FIELD~PROMO.NAME~3~Promotion Name~
FIELD~PROMO.DESC~4~Promotion Description~
FIELD~PROMO.TYPE~5~Promotion Type~DISCOUNT, BOGO, BUNDLE, FIXED_PRICE, LOYALTY, COUPON
FIELD~START.DATE~6~Start Date~
FIELD~START.TIME~7~Start Time~
FIELD~END.DATE~8~End Date~
FIELD~END.TIME~9~End Time~
FIELD~STATUS~10~Status~ACTIVE, INACTIVE, SCHEDULED, EXPIRED
FIELD~PRIORITY~11~Priority~1-10 (higher = higher priority)
FIELD~DISCOUNT.TYPE~12~Discount Type~PERCENT, AMOUNT, FIXED_PRICE
FIELD~DISCOUNT.VALUE~13~Discount Value~
FIELD~MAX.DISCOUNT~14~Maximum Discount Amount~
FIELD~MIN.PURCHASE~15~Minimum Purchase Amount~
FIELD~MAX.PURCHASE~16~Maximum Purchase Amount~
FIELD~APPLIES.TO~17~Applies To~ITEMS, CATEGORIES, BRANDS, TRANSACTION
FIELD~ITEM.IDS~18~Applicable Item IDs~Multivalued
FIELD~CATEGORIES~19~Applicable Categories~Multivalued
FIELD~BRANDS~20~Applicable Brands~Multivalued
FIELD~EXCLUDE.ITEMS~21~Excluded Item IDs~Multivalued
FIELD~EXCLUDE.CATEGORIES~22~Excluded Categories~Multivalued
FIELD~EXCLUDE.BRANDS~23~Excluded Brands~Multivalued
FIELD~BUY.QTY~24~Buy Quantity~For BOGO
FIELD~GET.QTY~25~Get Quantity~For BOGO
FIELD~GET.DISCOUNT~26~Get Discount Percentage~For BOGO
FIELD~BUNDLE.ITEMS~27~Bundle Item IDs~Multivalued
FIELD~BUNDLE.QTY~28~Bundle Quantities~Multivalued
FIELD~BUNDLE.PRICE~29~Bundle Price~
FIELD~STACKABLE~30~Stackable with Other Promos~Y/N
FIELD~COMBINABLE.WITH~31~Combinable Promotion IDs~Multivalued
FIELD~CUSTOMER.TYPE~32~Customer Type Restriction~R, W, C, or ALL
FIELD~LOYALTY.TIER~33~Loyalty Tier Restriction~BRONZE, SILVER, GOLD, PLATINUM, ALL
