* Index Definitions
INDEX~CODE.IDX~PROMO.CODE~Promotion Code Index
INDEX~STATUS.IDX~STATUS~Status Index
INDEX~START.DATE.IDX~START.DATE~Start Date Index
INDEX~END.DATE.IDX~END.DATE~End Date Index
INDEX~TYPE.IDX~PROMO.TYPE~Type Index

* Correlatives and Derived Fields
CORR~IS.ACTIVE~IF STATUS = 'ACTIVE' AND DATE() >= START.DATE AND DATE() <= END.DATE THEN 'Y' ELSE 'N'
CORR~DAYS.REMAINING~END.DATE - DATE()
CORR~DAYS.SINCE.START~DATE() - START.DATE
CORR~TOTAL.USES~USE.COUNT.TOTAL
CORR~USES.REMAINING~USE.LIMIT.TOTAL - USE.COUNT.TOTAL
CORR~BUDGET.VARIANCE~BUDGET.AMOUNT - ACTUAL.COST
CORR~BUDGET.PCT.USED~(ACTUAL.COST / BUDGET.AMOUNT) * 100
CORR~AVG.DISCOUNT.PER.USE~IF USE.COUNT.TOTAL > 0 THEN ACTUAL.COST / USE.COUNT.TOTAL ELSE 0
CORR~ROI~Revenue impact calculation (complex, defined in application)
